    "body": "Related to this I am also getting an issue with algoliasearch-helper typing when using setQueryParameter()\r\n\r\nArgument of type '\"maxValuesPerFacet\"' is not assignable to parameter of type 'keyof PlainSearchParameters'.\r\n\r\nYet according the documentation I should be able to use 'maxValuesPerFacet' and the code works.\r\n\r\nThe type definition is here https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/blob/62b6e4bbd27743cd0008548d7d59bd7cdb680b82/packages/algoliasearch-helper/index.d.ts#L654",
